Acceptance: Treat the authenticated Slack Socket Mode connection as the production trust boundary: obtain the rotating WSS URL only through apps.connections.open with the configured app-level token over TLS, validate hello app identity, envelope type and unique envelope_id, expected enterprise/team namespace and immutable user_id, acknowledge exactly once, and reject replayed, malformed, disconnected, mismatched-workspace, bot, or display-only evidence. If HTTP Events mode is later enabled it separately requires Slack signing-secret verification; it cannot inherit Socket Mode trust. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-13-github-user-attribution-and-feature-discovery.md.